            <p class="terms-sub-header"> 1. USER ANONYMITY </p>
            <p>Anonymous information may be disclosed at times regarding facts about user patterns. This information will only represent user statistics for advertising purposes. We do not know what you search for on search engines. We only know what you search for within our site.</p>
        
