            <p>Upon request to Revstance.com via the contact information stated on this page, Revstance.com shall inform you of the purpose of the processing; who receives the information and from where the information originates.</p>
            <p>Requests regarding the above shall only be processed if more than 6 months have lapsed since your previous request, unless you can substantiate a special interest in obtaining the information earlier.</p>

